@node "Register"
@title "AmigaGuideź. Professional Video Catalogue ©1993: Registration."

				@{b}@{u}E. REGISTRATION@{uu}@{ub}

   @{u}What do you get?@{uu}

 + Registered users  will  receive a  disk with the latest release of PVC.
   You may also be allowed  small discounts on further versions of PVC and
   of any Professional  Video tools  that may be released (see  @{" future " link "Future"})
   although this is not a right.

 + All features disabled in the demonstration of the same version will be
   enabled and  a palette more  conducive  for working  with used.  These 
   features include:-

	* Upto 1000 videos (memory permitting).
	* Upto 100 films per video (memory permitting).
	* Upto 26 entries  for Film Type, Channel, Video  Owner and Video
	  Make.
	* Ability to print out the video base to both printer and file.
	* Fully  embedded  security  with added privacy  as  required  by
          individual video owners.
	* ProTracker module support.
	* Videobase file encryption as required.
	* Configuration system  supporting default and  preset preference
	  files.
	* Auto videobase comment inheritance tagging.
	* A multitude of bug fixes.

   @{U}How to Register@{uu}

   In order to  receive the latest  full SHAREWARE  version you must first
   send a registration fee to the value of@{b} Ł6 sterling (British) + postage @{ub}
   of:-
